# CTG Tor/HTTP site rules — authorized lab use only (Hacker Planet LLC).
# Copy to /opt/ctg/tor-http-scrambler/site-rules.conf (mode 600).
# banking / financial sites → http (clearnet lab browser; your bank may block Tor)
# .onion → tor (always)

chase.com http
www.chase.com http
bankofamerica.com http
www.bankofamerica.com http
wellsfargo.com http
paypal.com http
.onion tor
